    "summary": "The user asks for travel advice regarding safe and upscale neighborhoods in Chicago, inquiring about which areas to avoid. The assistant provides suggestions and gradually moves from vague descriptions of \"well-to-do\" areas to explicitly linking a sense of \"order\" and safety to predominantly white, affluent neighborhoods versus \"cultural groups\" in low-income areas.",
